INSERT INTO Text VALUES (NULL,4,1443109011982,2,NULL,326176,'Neptune conjunct Pluto',NULL,'# Neptune conjunct Pluto\n\nThe combination of Pluto with Neptune gives masterful technical ability, especially in the arts, such as literature, film, and music. You know how to reach a mass audience. You are a good judge of quality and associate yourself with the best people. A girl with this aspect could appear virtuous but fiery. You combine tenderness with ferocity. With proper training, you could transform music, such as by rearranging a  piece originally composed for the piano for an orchestra. This aspect makes your work lush and elaborate. You can master a variety of skills. You like your freedom and would not like to be confined by a traditional system or even by traditional morals. You could be part of a network of friends who share modern concepts.  Your wide-ranging work could incidentally challenge contemporary cultural values and moral attitudes.  You are so big and all-encompassing that other people tend to project their narrow issues onto how they see you. Even if you are successful in a traditional career that makes your parents happy, you may, like the ancient philosopher Proclus, born in the year 412 with this aspect, switch to a career that makes better use of your universalistic mentality and which therefore makes you happy. If other aspects cause your chosen career to lie in the military, you will be a chivalrous and humane officer, and one who impresses his subordinates by seeming to know what the enemy is like and how they will react. There is a danger of self-absorption, of forgetting the ordinary people who support you, in which case you will pay a price. Last occurring in the late nineteenth century, this aspect will next occur from 2381 to 2390.','Charles E.O. Carter',0,0,'en',14,0,0);
INSERT INTO Text VALUES (NULL,4,1443109011983,2,NULL,26662,'Neptune conjunct Ascendant',NULL,'# Neptune conjunct Ascendant\n\nNeptune rising at the time of your birth will affect your life in an uncommon manner. You will be romantic and mediumistic, or psychically inclined. Some very strange experiences and also some remarkable episodes will occur in your life. It is only the very few who can in any way respond to the subtle, spiritual vibrations of the planet Neptune, and they are the souls that live the purest lives. You must be on your guard against hypnotic suggestion, and should be very selective in your associates and acquaintances. You will in all probability have some very remarkable dreams, which you should endeavor to remember. You will not escape being very mediumistic and hypersensitive at times.','Charles E.O. Carter',0,0,'en',14,0,0);
INSERT INTO Text VALUES (NULL,4,1443109011984,2,NULL,327712,'Neptune sextile Pluto',NULL,'# Neptune sextile Pluto\n\nThis aspect was present in many late 20th century charts. It may give a certain New Age awareness of community. It is not that important in an individual chart, except to give background awareness that we are all in it together, that it is as a community that we grow, thrive, and survive.','Charles E.O. Carter',0,0,'en',14,0,0);
INSERT INTO Text VALUES (NULL,4,1443109011985,2,NULL,328224,'Neptune square Pluto',NULL,'# Neptune square Pluto\n\nThe square last occurred between 1812 and 1824. It will occur again in the period from 2056 to 2059. The semi-square last occurred from 1929 to 1933. The sesquiquadrate last occurred from 1683 to 1691. Your far-reaching activities can be described as &ldquo;cosmopolitan&rdquo;; you don&apos;t know the meaning of the word &ldquo;barrier.&rdquo; You can be a dynamo of activity, and have some good ideas, but not everyone agrees with your way of looking at things. If you lack sensitivity, you will alienate the people whose support you need. Your ego might be such that your coworkers find you difficult to work with. Pluto intensifies Neptune&apos;s gift for abstract mathematics and music.','Charles E.O. Carter',0,0,'en',14,0,0);
INSERT INTO Text VALUES (NULL,4,1443109011986,2,NULL,328480,'Neptune trine Pluto',NULL,'# Neptune trine Pluto\n\nThis aspect has not been in effect since the 1700s. It will next occur in 2086. It may give a background awareness that it is in a community that we grow, thrive, and survive.','Charles E.O. Carter',0,0,'en',14,0,0);
INSERT INTO Text VALUES (NULL,4,1443109011987,2,NULL,329248,'Neptune opposite Pluto',NULL,'# Neptune opposite Pluto\n\nThe opposition last occurred from 1643 to 1648. This aspect will not occur again until the period 2133 to 2145. Your far-reaching activities can be described as &ldquo;cosmopolitan&rdquo;; you don&apos;t know the meaning of the word &ldquo;barrier.&rdquo; You can be a dynamo of activity, and have some good ideas, but not everyone agrees with your way of looking at things. If you lack sensitivity, you will alienate the people whose support you need. Your ego might be such that your coworkers find you difficult to work with. Pluto intensifies Neptune&apos;s gift for abstract mathematics and music.','Charles E.O. Carter',0,0,'en',14,0,0);
INSERT INTO Text VALUES (NULL,4,1443109011988,2,NULL,29990,'Pluto conjunct Ascendant',NULL,'# Pluto conjunct Ascendant\n\nWith Pluto rising, you like challenges.  You look for the biggest stone that you can find to move. You are a very capable person. You can master anything that you put your mind to. You could be a passionate supporter of causes or your team.','Charles E.O. Carter',0,0,'en',14,0,0);
